headline: Trump Tariffs Shift? Trump Denies, But Nucor, Enphase, Ford, FCX Lead S&P 500 Rally
summary: President-elect Trump denied a report that his tariffs may focus on strategic industries. But the S&P 500, Nucor, FCX, Enphase and Ford rose.
